OL,3,CFrom drapery to department store: 250
OL,4,Cyears of Hatchers
OL,6,FOne of the oldest family-owned
OL,7,Fdepartment stores in the UK is
OL,8,Fcelebrating its 250th birthday.
OL,10,FHatchers in Taunton was founded in
OL,11,FApril 1775, beginning its life as a
OL,12,Fdrapery business.
OL,14,FToday its owners say it is "thriving"
OL,15,Fon the town's High Street, employing
OL,16,Fmore than 40 people.
OL,18,FThe existing store location can track
OL,19,Fits roots to 1792.
