OL,6,FOne of the day books from that century
OL,7,Fis a prized possession of the present
OL,8,Fdirectors of the firm.
OL,10,FThe milestone is being marked with a
OL,11,Fcelebratory party for current and
OL,12,Fformer staff, which will be attended
OL,13,Fby the Lord-Lieutenant of Somerset,
OL,14,FMohammed Saddiq.
OL,16,FHatchers is owned by the Somerset-
OL,17,Fbased Hill and Raisey families, who
OL,18,Ftook over in 1986.
