OL,3,CFrom drapery to department store: 250
OL,4,Cyears of Hatchers
OL,6,FThey can trace their own family roots
OL,7,Fin Hatchers back to the 1960s and
OL,8,Fearly 1970s, when members of both
OL,9,Ffamilies were directors of the store.
OL,11,FMike Hill and Clive Raisey, who were
OL,12,Falready shareholders in the company,
OL,13,Fsaid taking full ownership was a huge
OL,14,Fdecision at the time, but one that has
OL,15,Fmade them extremely proud.
OL,17,F"Predatory development and investment
OL,18,Fcompanies were circling to buy
OL,19,FHatchers at the time. But we wanted it
OL,20,Fto stay local," Mr Hill said.
