OL,6,FMr Hill and Mr Raisey's sons, Stephen
OL,7,Fand Mark, are now directors of the
OL,8,Fbusiness and the connection continues
OL,9,Fas other family members are also
OL,10,Finvolved.
OL,12,FStephen Hill said: "The Hatchers story
OL,13,Fis really unique in today's business
OL,14,Fworld. What other store can talk of
OL,15,Fsuch history?
OL,17,F"And I am proud to be part owner of
OL,18,Fthe company now."
