OL,6,FMark Raisey added: "It is a fantastic
OL,7,Fpast but I believe we also have a
OL,8,Fbright future. The people of Taunton,
OL,9,Fand much further afield, continue to
OL,10,Fsupport us.
OL,12,F"We have a fantastically loyal
OL,13,Fcustomer base, so we look forward to
OL,14,Four 300th birthday."
OL,16,FNelson, Napoleon, Washington and
OL,17,FWellington and other giants of history
OL,18,Fwere alive when Hatchers was born in
OL,19,F1775.
